name: JournalJar
0:
”Alexa, open Journal Jar”
”Alexa, ask Journal Jar for today's prompt”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: journal jar
des: Journal Jar is a quick & easy way to get the creative juices flowing when you’re stuck trying to decide what to journal about. Each day, you’ll get a new journal prompt to get you started.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
